<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Spiritus | VPN Management Panel</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg0:#050810;--bg1:#0a0f1a;--bg2:#111827;--bg3:#1a2035;--bg4:#232b42;
  --border:#1e2a45;--border2:#2d3f6a;
  --t0:#eaf0f9;--t1:#bcc8db;--t2:#7a8ba8;--t3:#546380;
  --accent:#6c9fff;--accent2:#3b7cf5;--accent-glow:rgba(59,124,245,.25);
  --green:#34d399;--green-bg:rgba(52,211,153,.12);
  --yellow:#fbbf24;--yellow-bg:rgba(251,191,36,.1);
  --red:#f87171;--red-bg:rgba(248,113,113,.1);
  --purple:#a78bfa;--orange:#fb923c;
  --glass:rgba(17,24,39,.55);--glass-border:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  --radius:16px;--radius-sm:12px;--radius-xs:8px;
  --shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.45);--shadow-lg:0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
  --glow:0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
  --transition:.25s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--bg0);color:var(--t1);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;
  background-image:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -20%,rgba(59,124,245,.08),transparent)}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--bg4);border-radius:10px}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{background:var(--border2)}
input,button,textarea,select{font-family:inherit;font-size:inherit}
::selection{background:var(--accent2);color:#fff}

/* ── Login ── */
#login-screen{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  background:#050810}
#login-screen::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%,rgba(59,124,245,.15),transparent 50%),
             radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 60%,rgba(167,139,250,.1),transparent 50%),
             radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 90%,rgba(52,211,153,.08),transparent 40%);
  animation:loginBg 15s ease infinite alternate}
@keyframes loginBg{0%{opacity:.8;transform:scale(1)}100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1.05)}}
.login-card{position:relative;background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:20px;
  padding:52px 44px;width:400px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);z-index:1;
  animation:loginCardIn .6s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
@keyframes loginCardIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) scale(.96)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0) scale(1)}}
.login-logo{font-size:48px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:6px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700 0%,#FFA500 50%,#FFD700 100%);background-size:200% 200%;
  -webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;color:transparent;
  animation:logoShift 6s ease infinite;margin-bottom:6px;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,.4))}
@keyframes logoShift{0%,100%{background-position:0% 50%}50%{background-position:100% 50%}}
.login-sub{color:var(--t2);margin-bottom:36px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.login-input{width:100%;padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(10,15,26,.6);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);color:var(--t0);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:18px;
  text-align:center;letter-spacing:3px;transition:var(--transition)}
.login-input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow)}
.login-btn{width:100%;padding:15px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#DAA520);color:#1a1a2e;border:none;
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition);
  letter-spacing:.5px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.login-btn::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.1));
  opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
.login-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(255,215,0,.45)}
.login-btn:hover::before{opacity:1}
.login-btn:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.login-error{color:var(--red);margin-top:14px;font-size:13px;min-height:20px;font-weight:500}

/* ── Panel ── */
#panel{display:none}
.top-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 28px;
  background:rgba(10,15,26,.75);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,215,0,.15);border-top:2px solid #FFD700;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
  box-shadow:0 1px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.brand-logo{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:4px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#FFA500,#FFD700,#DAA520);background-size:200% 200%;
  -webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;color:transparent;
  animation:logoShift 6s ease infinite}
.brand-text{color:var(--t3);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px}
.header-actions{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}

.btn{padding:10px 20px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;
  cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.btn::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.05),transparent);
  opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}.btn:hover::after{opacity:1}
.btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#DAA520);color:#1a1a2e;
  box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(59,124,245,.2)}
.btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(255,215,0,.45)}
.btn-outline{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--t1);
  backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);background:rgba(108,159,255,.06)}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--t2);padding:10px 14px}.btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--t0)}
.btn-danger{background:rgba(248,113,113,.08);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.2)}
.btn-danger:hover{border-color:var(--red);background:rgba(248,113,113,.15);box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(248,113,113,.15)}
.btn-sm{padding:7px 14px;font-size:12px;border-radius:var(--radius-xs)}
.btn-green{background:rgba(52,211,153,.08);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2)}
.btn-green:hover{border-color:var(--green);background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(52,211,153,.15)}
.btn-orange{background:rgba(251,146,60,.08);color:var(--orange);border:1px solid rgba(251,146,60,.2)}
.btn-orange:hover{border-color:var(--orange);background:rgba(251,146,60,.15)}

/* ── Stats Bar ── */
.stats-bar{display:flex;gap:0;padding:0;background:rgba(10,15,26,.5);border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
.stat-item{flex:1;padding:20px 20px;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  transition:var(--transition);position:relative}
.stat-item:last-child{border-right:none}
.stat-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.stat-value{display:block;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:var(--t0);
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--t0),var(--t1));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;color:transparent}
.stat-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;font-weight:600}

/* ── Protocol Badges ── */
.proto-bar{display:flex;gap:6px;padding:10px 28px;background:rgba(10,15,26,.3);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.proto-badge{padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;transition:var(--transition);
  backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.proto-badge:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}
.proto-vmess{background:rgba(108,159,255,.1);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid rgba(108,159,255,.15)}
.proto-vless{background:rgba(167,139,250,.1);color:var(--purple);border:1px solid rgba(167,139,250,.15)}
.proto-cdn{background:rgba(251,146,60,.1);color:var(--orange);border:1px solid rgba(251,146,60,.15)}
.proto-ks{background:rgba(52,211,153,.1);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.15)}
.proto-ks.off{background:rgba(248,113,113,.1);color:var(--red);border-color:rgba(248,113,113,.15)}

/* ── Grid ── */
.container{padding:24px 28px}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:18px}

/* ── User Card ── */
.card{background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:22px;transition:var(--transition);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent2),var(--purple),var(--green));opacity:.4;transition:opacity .3s}
.card:hover{border-color:var(--border);transform:translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.35),0 0 0 1px var(--glass-border)}
.card:hover::before{opacity:.8}
.card.inactive{opacity:.45;filter:saturate(.5)}
.card.inactive:hover{opacity:.6;filter:saturate(.7)}
.card-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px}
.card-name{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.online-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--t3);transition:all .4s}
.online-dot.on{background:var(--green);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--green),0 0 20px rgba(52,211,153,.3);animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--green),0 0 20px rgba(52,211,153,.3)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 5px var(--green),0 0 10px rgba(52,211,153,.15)}}
.user-name{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t0);letter-spacing:.2px}
.badge{padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.badge-active{background:rgba(52,211,153,.1);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2)}
.badge-inactive{background:rgba(248,113,113,.08);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.15)}

.traffic-section{margin-bottom:14px}
.progress-track{height:6px;background:var(--bg4);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;position:relative}
.progress-fill{height:100%;border-radius:6px;transition:width 1s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1),background .5s;position:relative}
.progress-fill::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.2),transparent);animation:shimmer 2.5s infinite}
@keyframes shimmer{0%{transform:translateX(-100%)}100%{transform:translateX(100%)}}
.traffic-text{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;color:var(--t2)}
.traffic-text b{color:var(--t0)}

.info-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--t2);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.info-row:last-of-type{border-bottom:none}
.info-row .val{color:var(--t1);font-weight:600}
.info-row .warn{color:var(--yellow);font-weight:700}
.info-row .crit{color:var(--red);font-weight:700;animation:critPulse 2s ease infinite}
@keyframes critPulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.7}}

.speed-row{display:flex;gap:16px;margin:12px 0;padding:10px 14px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)}
.speed-item{flex:1;text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);font-weight:500}
.speed-val{display:block;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t0);margin-top:2px}
.speed-item.up .speed-val{color:var(--green)}
.speed-item.down .speed-val{color:var(--accent)}

.card-actions{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:14px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border);flex-wrap:wrap}
.card-actions .btn{flex:1;justify-content:center;min-width:calc(33% - 4px)}

/* ── Modals ── */
.modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);
  backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px);z-index:200;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px}
.modal-overlay.show{display:flex}
.modal{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:20px;
  padding:32px;width:100%;max-width:440px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);
  animation:modalIn .35s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.modal::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(108,159,255,.3),transparent)}
.modal-lg{max-width:560px}
.modal-xl{max-width:700px}
@keyframes modalIn{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(.92) translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1) translateY(0)}}
.modal h3{font-size:18px;color:var(--t0);margin-bottom:24px;font-weight:700;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.form-group{margin-bottom:18px}
.form-group label{display:block;font-size:12px;color:var(--t2);margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.3px}
.form-group input,.form-group select{width:100%;padding:12px 16px;background:rgba(10,15,26,.5);
  border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);color:var(--t0);font-size:14px;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.form-group input:focus,.form-group select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow)}
.modal-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:24px}
.modal-actions .btn{flex:1;justify-content:center;padding:12px}

/* Config modal */
.config-tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:20px;background:rgba(10,15,26,.4);padding:4px}
.config-tab{flex:1;padding:10px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
  background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--t3);transition:var(--transition);border-radius:var(--radius-xs);
  letter-spacing:.3px}
.config-tab:hover{color:var(--t1);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.config-tab.active{color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
.config-tab.tab-vmess.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent))}
.config-tab.tab-vless.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#a78bfa)}
.config-tab.tab-cdn.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ea580c,var(--orange))}
.qr-box{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:18px;display:inline-block;margin:0 auto 20px;
  box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
.qr-box svg{display:block}
.config-center{text-align:center}
.vmess-box{margin-top:16px}
.vmess-box textarea{width:100%;padding:12px;background:rgba(10,15,26,.5);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);color:var(--accent);font-size:11px;font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,Consolas,monospace;
  resize:none;direction:ltr;text-align:left;word-break:break-all}
.config-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-top:16px;
  padding:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:12px}
.config-grid .ck{color:var(--t3)}.config-grid .cv{color:var(--t1);direction:ltr;text-align:left}

/* ── Toast ── */
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:24px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(100px);
  padding:14px 28px;background:var(--bg2);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:var(--radius);
  color:var(--t0);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;z-index:999;
  transition:transform .4s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),opacity .4s;opacity:0;
  box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg)}
.toast.show{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0);opacity:1}
.toast.error{border-color:rgba(248,113,113,.3);color:var(--red);box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(248,113,113,.15)}

/* ── Activity Modal ── */
.activity-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px}
.activity-header h3{margin-bottom:0}
.live-dot{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;color:var(--green);font-weight:700;
  letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.live-dot::before{content:'';width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);
  box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--green);animation:livePulse 1.5s ease infinite}
@keyframes livePulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--green)}50%{opacity:.5;box-shadow:0 0 4px var(--green)}}
.activity-tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(10,15,26,.4);padding:3px}
.activity-tab{flex:1;padding:9px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;
  background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--t3);transition:var(--transition);border-radius:var(--radius-xs)}
.activity-tab.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent));color:#fff;
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(59,124,245,.25)}
.activity-body{max-height:400px;overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch}
.site-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  font-size:13px;transition:var(--transition);flex-wrap:wrap}
.site-row:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.site-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.site-host{flex:1;color:var(--t0);font-weight:500;word-break:break-all;font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,monospace;font-size:12px}
.site-port{color:var(--t3);font-size:11px;min-width:48px;text-align:right}
.site-count{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;font-size:13px;min-width:36px;text-align:right}
.site-time{color:var(--t3);font-size:11px;min-width:60px;text-align:right}
.site-svc{font-size:10px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;
  backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}
.activity-total{padding:12px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--t3);border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border);margin-top:8px}
.activity-empty{text-align:center;padding:40px 20px;color:var(--t3);font-size:14px}
.alert-banner{padding:12px 16px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:12px;font-size:12px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:500;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.alert-danger{background:rgba(248,81,73,.1);border:1px solid rgba(248,81,73,.3);color:var(--red)}
.alert-warning{background:rgba(210,153,34,.1);border:1px solid rgba(210,153,34,.3);color:var(--yellow)}
.alert-icon{font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0}
.alert-text{flex:1;line-height:1.4}
.alert-count{font-weight:700;font-size:14px}
.site-flag{min-width:22px;text-align:center;font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0}
.site-geo{color:var(--t3);font-size:10px;min-width:28px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0}
.site-org{color:var(--t3);font-size:10px;max-width:120px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
.site-row.row-danger{background:rgba(248,81,73,.06);border-left:3px solid var(--red)}
.site-row.row-danger .site-host{color:var(--red)}
.site-row.row-warning{background:rgba(210,153,34,.05);border-left:3px solid var(--yellow)}
.recent-row{padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);font-size:12px;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.recent-row:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.recent-row.row-danger{background:rgba(248,81,73,.06);border-left:3px solid var(--red)}
.recent-time{color:var(--t3);min-width:55px;font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,monospace;font-size:11px}
.recent-flag{min-width:18px;font-size:12px}
.recent-host{color:var(--t0);font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,monospace;word-break:break-all;flex:1}
.recent-port{color:var(--accent);font-size:11px}
.recent-geo{color:var(--t3);font-size:10px;min-width:24px}
.recent-svc{font-size:9px;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}

/* ── Analysis Tab ── */
.analysis-section{margin-bottom:20px}
.analysis-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--t0);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.analysis-title .at-icon{font-size:15px}
.behavior-summary{background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
.behavior-line{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:5px 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--t1);line-height:1.5}
.behavior-line .bl-icon{font-size:15px;min-width:20px;text-align:center}
.behavior-line .bl-risk{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;margin-left:auto;flex-shrink:0}
.risk-danger{background:rgba(248,81,73,.12);color:var(--red)}
.risk-watch{background:rgba(227,179,65,.12);color:var(--yellow)}
.cat-bar-wrap{margin-bottom:10px}
.cat-bar-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:5px}
.cat-bar-name{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--t1)}
.cat-bar-name .cb-icon{font-size:14px}
.cat-bar-pct{font-size:12px;font-weight:700}
.cat-bar-track{height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}
.cat-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;transition:width .6s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(108,159,255,.2)}
.cat-bar-services{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin-top:5px}
.cat-svc-chip{font-size:10px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);color:var(--t2);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);transition:var(--transition)}
.cat-svc-chip:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.07)}
.svc-table{width:100%}
.svc-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);font-size:12px;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.svc-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.svc-row:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.svc-rank{color:var(--t3);min-width:20px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;font-size:11px}
.svc-icon{font-size:14px;min-width:20px;text-align:center}
.svc-name{flex:1;color:var(--t0);font-weight:500}
.svc-cat{font-size:10px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:500}
.svc-count{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;min-width:40px;text-align:right}
.svc-risk-tag{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:5px}

/* ── Deep Analysis ── */
.deep-section{margin-top:20px;border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border);padding-top:16px}
.deep-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--t0);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.verdict-box{padding:14px 18px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.verdict-safe{background:rgba(46,160,67,.1);border:1px solid rgba(46,160,67,.3);color:var(--green);
  box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(46,160,67,.08)}
.verdict-watch{background:rgba(210,153,34,.1);border:1px solid rgba(210,153,34,.3);color:var(--yellow);
  box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(210,153,34,.08)}
.verdict-danger{background:rgba(248,81,73,.1);border:1px solid rgba(248,81,73,.3);color:var(--red);
  box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(248,81,73,.08)}
.activity-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);font-size:12px;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.activity-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.activity-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.ai-icon{font-size:16px;min-width:22px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:1px}
.ai-text{flex:1;line-height:1.5}
.ai-action{color:var(--t0);font-weight:500;display:block}
.ai-host{color:var(--t3);font-size:11px;font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,monospace}
.ai-count{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;font-size:12px;min-width:40px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0}
.port-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 12px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  transition:var(--transition)}
.port-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.port-row:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.port-num{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;min-width:50px;font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,monospace}
.port-desc{flex:1;color:var(--t1)}
.port-count{color:var(--t3);min-width:40px;text-align:right}
.deep-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px}
.deep-stat{background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:12px 16px;text-align:center;transition:var(--transition)}
.deep-stat:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.deep-stat-val{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t0);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),#a78bfa);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;color:transparent}
.deep-stat-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:3px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.3px}

/* ── Filter Bar ── */
.filter-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 28px;
  background:rgba(10,15,26,.4);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);overflow-x:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch}
.filter-bar::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.filter-pills{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-shrink:0}
.filter-pill{padding:8px 18px;border-radius:24px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;
  border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--t3);transition:var(--transition);
  white-space:nowrap;user-select:none;letter-spacing:.3px}
.filter-pill:hover{border-color:var(--border2);color:var(--t1);background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.filter-pill.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent));
  border-color:transparent;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(59,124,245,.25)}
.filter-pill .pill-count{display:inline-block;min-width:18px;height:18px;line-height:18px;
  text-align:center;border-radius:9px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;margin-left:6px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.12)}
.filter-pill.active .pill-count{background:rgba(255,255,255,.25)}
.filter-search{flex:1;min-width:140px;max-width:280px;margin-left:auto;padding:9px 16px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:24px;
  color:var(--t0);font-size:13px;transition:var(--transition)}
.filter-search:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow)}
.filter-search::placeholder{color:var(--t3)}

/* ── Bulk modal header (ZIP always visible without scrolling) ── */
.bulk-modal-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px}
.bulk-zip-top{flex-shrink:0;white-space:nowrap}

/* ── Bulk QR grid ── */
.bulk-qr-section{margin-top:16px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
.bulk-qr-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:14px;max-height:420px;overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;padding:4px 0}
.bulk-qr-card{background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:14px;transition:var(--transition)}
.bulk-qr-card:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.bulk-qr-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t0);margin-bottom:10px}
.bulk-qr-title small{font-weight:600;color:var(--t3);margin-left:6px}
.bulk-qr-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:flex-start}
.bulk-qr-item{text-align:center}
.bulk-qr-lbl{display:block;font-size:10px;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:600}
.bulk-qr-item svg{display:block;margin:0 auto;border-radius:8px;background:#fff;padding:6px;
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}

/* ── Bulk Tabs ── */
.bulk-tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:10px 0 12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:4px}
.bulk-tab{padding:7px 14px;border-radius:var(--radius-xs);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
  border:none;background:transparent;color:var(--t3);transition:var(--transition);user-select:none}
.bulk-tab:hover{color:var(--t1);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.bulk-tab.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent));color:#fff;
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(59,124,245,.25)}
.bulk-tab small{opacity:.8;font-weight:600}

/* ── Settings Section ── */
.settings-tab-content{display:none}
.settings-tab-content.active{display:block}
.settings-section{margin-bottom:24px;border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:18px;background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);position:relative;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.settings-section:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.settings-section::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent),transparent);border-radius:var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;opacity:.6}
.settings-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t2);margin-bottom:14px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.settings-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
.settings-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.settings-label{font-size:14px;color:var(--t1)}
.settings-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.4}

/* ── Status indicators ── */
.st-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:6px;flex-shrink:0;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.st-dot.on{background:var(--green);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(46,160,67,.5)}
.st-dot.off{background:var(--red);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(248,81,73,.5)}
.st-dot.warn{background:var(--yellow);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(227,179,65,.5)}
.st-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;
  backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}
.st-badge.on{background:rgba(46,160,67,.12);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(46,160,67,.2)}
.st-badge.off{background:rgba(248,81,73,.1);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(248,81,73,.2)}
.st-badge.warn{background:rgba(227,179,65,.1);color:var(--yellow);border:1px solid rgba(227,179,65,.2)}

/* ── Bilingual help boxes ── */
.help-box{margin-top:10px;padding:14px 16px;background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:12px;line-height:1.7}
.help-box .help-en{color:var(--t2);direction:ltr;text-align:left}
.help-box .help-fa{color:var(--t1);direction:rtl;text-align:right;font-family:'Vazirmatn',Tahoma,sans-serif;margin-top:6px;padding-top:6px;border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
.help-box b{color:var(--accent)}
.help-box code{color:var(--green);background:rgba(5,8,16,.6);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
.help-title{font-weight:700;color:var(--t0);margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}

/* ── Section header with status ── */
.sec-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.sec-header .settings-title{margin-bottom:0}
.s-indicator{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;white-space:nowrap;
  backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}
.s-indicator.on{background:rgba(46,160,67,.12);color:#3fb950;border:1px solid rgba(46,160,67,.2)}
.s-indicator.off{background:rgba(248,81,73,.1);color:#f85149;border:1px solid rgba(248,81,73,.2)}
.s-indicator.info{background:rgba(56,139,253,.1);color:#58a6ff;border:1px solid rgba(56,139,253,.2)}
.s-indicator .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.s-indicator.on .dot{background:#3fb950;box-shadow:0 0 8px #3fb95088}
.s-indicator.off .dot{background:#f85149}
.s-indicator.info .dot{background:#58a6ff}
.s-help{margin-top:10px;padding:14px;background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;border-left:3px solid var(--accent);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-left:3px solid var(--accent)}
.s-help .fa{font-size:14px;color:var(--accent);margin-right:4px}
.s-help-toggle{cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);margin-left:auto;user-select:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.s-help-toggle:hover{color:var(--t0)}
.s-help b{color:var(--t1)}
.s-help .en{color:var(--t2)}
.s-help .fa{color:var(--t3);direction:rtl;text-align:right;display:block;margin-top:4px}
.toggle{position:relative;width:46px;height:24px;cursor:pointer}
.toggle input{opacity:0;width:0;height:0}
.toggle-slider{position:absolute;inset:0;background:var(--bg4);border-radius:12px;transition:.3s;
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
.toggle-slider::before{content:'';position:absolute;height:18px;width:18px;left:3px;bottom:2px;
  background:var(--t2);border-radius:50%;transition:.3s}
.toggle input:checked+.toggle-slider{background:var(--green);border-color:rgba(46,160,67,.3);
  box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(46,160,67,.3)}
.toggle input:checked+.toggle-slider::before{transform:translateX(20px);background:#fff}
.backup-item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 16px;
  background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:8px;font-size:13px;transition:var(--transition)}
.backup-item:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.backup-name{color:var(--t1);font-weight:500;font-family:monospace;font-size:12px}
.backup-meta{color:var(--t3);font-size:11px}

/* ── System Monitor Bar ── */
.sysmon-bar{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  background:rgba(10,15,26,.5);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);overflow-x:auto}
.sysmon-item{flex:1;padding:12px 16px;border-right:1px solid var(--glass-border);min-width:110px;text-align:center;
  transition:var(--transition)}
.sysmon-item:last-child{border-right:none}
.sysmon-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.sysmon-val{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t0)}
.sysmon-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--t3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-top:3px}
.sysmon-bar .gauge{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:2px;
  border:2px solid transparent;transition:var(--transition)}
.gauge-ok{background:rgba(46,160,67,.1);color:#3fb950;border-color:rgba(46,160,67,.25);
  box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(46,160,67,.1)}
.gauge-warn{background:rgba(227,179,65,.1);color:#e3b341;border-color:rgba(227,179,65,.25);
  box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(227,179,65,.1)}
.gauge-crit{background:rgba(248,81,73,.1);color:#f85149;border-color:rgba(248,81,73,.25);
  box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(248,81,73,.1);animation:critPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}

/* ── User Note Badge ── */
.note-badge{display:inline-block;max-width:180px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;
  font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);padding:3px 10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);
  border:1px solid var(--glass-border);border-radius:10px;margin-top:4px;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition)}
.note-badge:hover{color:var(--t1);background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border-color:var(--border2)}

/* ── Online IPs Badge ── */
.ip-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-size:10px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:10px;
  background:rgba(56,139,253,.08);color:#58a6ff;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid rgba(56,139,253,.15);
  transition:var(--transition);backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}
.ip-badge:hover{background:rgba(56,139,253,.15);border-color:rgba(56,139,253,.3)}

/* ── Add Traffic ── */
.add-traffic-inline{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;margin-top:6px}
.add-traffic-inline input{width:60px;padding:5px 8px;font-size:11px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
  border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;color:var(--t1);transition:var(--transition)}
.add-traffic-inline input:focus{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 2px var(--accent-glow)}

/* ── Traffic History Chart ── */
.traffic-chart{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:2px;height:100px;padding:12px 0}
.traffic-chart-bar{flex:1;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;min-width:6px;transition:height .3s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  cursor:pointer;position:relative;opacity:.85}
.traffic-chart-bar:hover{opacity:1;box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(108,159,255,.3)}
.traffic-chart-bar:hover::after{content:attr(data-tip);position:absolute;bottom:100%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  background:rgba(10,15,26,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  color:var(--t1);padding:5px 10px;border-radius:8px;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap;z-index:10}
.traffic-chart-labels{display:flex;gap:2px;font-size:8px;color:var(--t3)}
.traffic-chart-labels span{flex:1;text-align:center}

/* ── Online Users Table ── */
.online-tbl{width:100%;font-size:12px;border-collapse:collapse}
.online-tbl th{text-align:left;padding:9px 12px;color:var(--t3);font-weight:600;font-size:11px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.3px}
.online-tbl td{padding:7px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03);color:var(--t1);
  transition:var(--transition)}
.online-tbl tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}

/* ── Empty State ── */
.empty{text-align:center;padding:80px 20px;color:var(--t3)}
.empty-icon{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px;opacity:.6}
.empty-text{font-size:15px;line-height:1.5}

/* ── Agent Management ── */
.agent-card{background:var(--glass);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border:1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:16px;margin-bottom:10px;transition:var(--transition);position:relative}
.agent-card:hover{border-color:var(--border2);transform:translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}
.agent-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent),transparent);border-radius:var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0 0;opacity:.5}
.agent-card-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:10px}
.agent-card-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t0)}
.agent-quota-bar{height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;margin:8px 0}
.agent-quota-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;transition:width .6s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(108,159,255,.15)}
.agent-info{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;color:var(--t2);margin-bottom:8px}
.agent-actions{display:flex;gap:6px}

/* ── Responsive ── */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .top-bar{flex-direction:column;gap:12px;padding:14px 16px}
  .header-actions{width:100%;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .stats-bar{flex-wrap:wrap}.stat-item{min-width:50%;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
  .proto-bar{padding:8px 16px}
  .filter-bar{padding:10px 16px;gap:8px}
  .filter-search{min-width:100px;max-width:180px}
  .container{padding:16px}
  .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px}
  .modal-overlay{padding:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding-top:20px}
  .modal{padding:20px 16px;margin:0;max-height:calc(100vh - 40px);overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;
    backdrop-filter:blur(16px)}
  .modal-lg,.modal-xl{max-width:100%}
  .modal h3{font-size:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .qr-box{padding:10px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .qr-box svg{max-width:180px;max-height:180px;width:100%;height:auto}
  .vmess-box textarea{font-size:10px;padding:10px}
  .config-grid{grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:6px 10px;padding:10px;font-size:11px}
  .config-grid .cv{word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word}
  .modal-actions{flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
  .modal-actions .btn{width:100%}
  .card-actions{flex-wrap:wrap}
  .card-actions .btn{min-width:calc(50% - 4px)}
  .sysmon-bar{flex-wrap:wrap}
  .sysmon-item{min-width:33%;border-bottom:1px solid var(--glass-border)}
  .settings-section{padding:14px}
  .bulk-qr-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .deep-stats{grid-template-columns:1fr}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── Login ── -->
<div id="login-screen">
  <div class="login-card">
    <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='logo.png') }}" alt="Spiritus Logo" style="width:220px;height:auto;margin:0 auto 20px;display:block;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(255,215,0,.6))">
    <div class="login-logo">SPIRITUS</div>
    <div class="login-sub">Premium VPN Management</div>
    <input type="password" id="login-pass" class="login-input" placeholder="Password"
           onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')doLogin()">
    <button type="button" class="login-btn" id="login-submit" onclick="doLogin()">Sign In</button>
    <div class="login-error" id="login-error"></div>
    <a href="/agent" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:18px;color:var(--t3);font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--accent)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--t3)'">Agent Panel →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Panel ── -->
<div id="panel">
  <header class="top-bar">
    <div class="brand">
      <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='logo.png') }}" alt="Spiritus" style="width:42px;height:auto;background:transparent">
      <span class="brand-logo">SPIRITUS</span>
      <span class="brand-text">VPN Management Panel</span>
    </div>
    <div class="header-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="forceSync()">Sync</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="showModal('add-modal')">+ Add User</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('bulk-modal')">Bulk Configs</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" id="btn-groups" onclick="switchMainView('groups')">Groups</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" id="btn-users" onclick="switchMainView('users')" style="display:none">Users</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('agents-modal')">Agents</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('sysmon-modal')" title="System Monitor">Monitor</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('online-modal')" title="Online Users & IPs">Online IPs</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('search-modal')" title="Search Users">🔍 Search</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('report-modal')" title="Statistics Report">📊 Report</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('analytics-modal')" title="Traffic Analytics">📈 Analytics</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="showModal('backup-modal')" title="Backup & Restore">💾 Backup</button>
      <button class="btn btn-orange btn-sm" onclick="showModal('aggressive-modal')" title="Resilience">⚔️ Resilience</button>
      <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onclick="showModal('fightback-modal')" title="Fight Back">🛡️ Fight Back</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="doExportCSV()" title="Export CSV">CSV</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="doExportJSON()" title="Export JSON">JSON</button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="showModal('settings-modal')">Settings</button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="doLogout()">Logout</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- System Monitor Bar -->
  <div class="sysmon-bar" id="sysmon-bar">
    <div class="sysmon-item"><div class="gauge gauge-ok" id="sm-cpu-gauge">—</div><div class="sysmon-lbl">CPU</div></div>
    <div class="sysmon-item"><div class="gauge gauge-ok" id="sm-ram-gauge">—</div><div class="sysmon-lbl">RAM</div></div>
    <div class="sysmon-item"><div class="gauge gauge-ok" id="sm-disk-gauge">—</div><div class="sysmon-lbl">Disk</div></div>
    <div class="sysmon-item"><div class="sysmon-val" id="sm-uptime">—</div><div class="sysmon-lbl">Uptime</div></div>
    <div class="sysmon-item"><div class="sysmon-val" id="sm-xray">—</div><div class="sysmon-lbl">Xray</div></div>
    <div class="sysmon-item"><div class="sysmon-val" id="sm-net">—</div><div class="sysmon-lbl">Network I/O</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-value" id="s-total">—</span><span class="stat-label">Total Users</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-value" id="s-active">—</span><span class="stat-label">Active</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-value" id="s-online">—</span><span class="stat-label">Online</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-value" id="s-traffic">—</span><span class="stat-label">Total Traffic</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="proto-bar" id="proto-bar" style="flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px">
    <span class="proto-badge proto-vmess" id="pb-vmess">VMess:443</span>
    <span class="proto-badge proto-vless" id="pb-vless" style="display:none">VLESS/Reality</span>
    <span class="proto-badge proto-cdn" id="pb-cdn" style="display:none">CDN</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-trojan" style="display:none;background:#e74c3c22;color:#e74c3c">Trojan</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-grpc" style="display:none;background:#2ecc7122;color:#2ecc71">gRPC</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-httpupgrade" style="display:none;background:#3498db22;color:#3498db">HU</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-ss2022" style="display:none;background:#e67e2222;color:#e67e22">SS2022</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-vless-ws" style="display:none;background:#1abc9c22;color:#1abc9c">VLESS-WS</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-fragment" style="display:none;background:#f39c1222;color:#f39c12">Fragment</span>
    <span class="proto-badge" id="pb-mux" style="display:none;background:#9b59b622;color:#9b59b6">MUX</span>
    <span class="proto-badge proto-ks" id="pb-ks">Kill Switch: ON</span>
  </div>

  <div class="filter-bar">
    <div class="filter-pills" id="filter-pills">
      <button class="filter-pill active" data-filter="all">All<span class="pill-count" id="fc-all">0</span></button>
      <button class="filter-pill" data-filter="online">Online<span class="pill-count" id="fc-online">0</span></button>
      <button class="filter-pill" data-filter="offline">Offline<span class="pill-count" id="fc-offline">0</span></button>
      <button class="filter-pill" data-filter="active">Active<span class="pill-count" id="fc-active">0</span></button>
      <button class="filter-pill" data-filter="disabled">Disabled<span class="pill-count" id="fc-disabled">0</span></button>
      <button class="filter-pill" data-filter="expiring">Expiring<span class="pill-count" id="fc-expiring">0</span></button>
    </div>
    <input type="text" class="filter-search" id="filter-search" placeholder="Search user..." oninput="applyFilter()">
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div id="users-grid" class="grid"></div>
    <div id="groups-grid" class="grid" style="display:none"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Add Modal ── -->
<div id="add-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeModal(this.id)">
  <div class="modal">
    <h3>New User</h3>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Username</label>
      <input type="text" id="add-name" placeholder="e.g. ali"></div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Traffic (GB)</label>
      <input type="number" id="add-traffic" value="10" min="0.1" step="0.1"></div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Duration (days)</label>
      <input type="number" id="add-days" value="30" min="1"></div>
    <div class="form-group" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px">
      <div><label>Speed Down (KB/s)</label>
        <input type="number" id="add-speed-down" value="200" min="0"></div>
      <div><label>Speed Up (KB/s)</label>
        <input type="number" id="add-speed-up" value="200" min="0"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Note</label>
      <input type="text" id="add-note" placeholder="Optional note..." maxlength="500"></div>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="doAddUser()">Create User</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="closeModal('add-modal')">Cancel</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Bulk Modal ── -->
<div id="bulk-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeModal(this.id)">
  <div class="modal modal-xl" style="max-height:calc(100vh - 40px);overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch">
    <div class="bulk-modal-head">
      <h3 style="margin:0">Bulk Configs (Group)</h3>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-green btn-sm bulk-zip-top" onclick="downloadBulkZip()" title="One .txt per user + ALL-CONFIGS.txt">Download ZIP</button>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:12px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:12px;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px">
      Default mode creates users <b style="color:var(--t1)">without applying to server</b>, so existing connected configs won't drop.
      You can apply later via <b style="color:var(--t1)">Sync</b>.
      <br><br>
      Output uses <code style="color:var(--accent)">&lt;&lt;&lt;BEGIN:name&gt;&gt;&gt;</code> … <code style="color:var(--accent)">&lt;&lt;&lt;END:name&gt;&gt;&gt;</code> for one-block copy. Prefer <b style="color:var(--t1)">Download ZIP</b>: one <code>.txt</code> per user plus <code>ALL-CONFIGS.txt</code>, clearly spaced.
    </div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Prefix (group name)</label>
      <input type="text" id="bulk-prefix" value="group" placeholder="e.g. 1gig"></div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Count</label>
      <input type="number" id="bulk-count" value="10" min="1" max="500"></div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Traffic per user (GB)</label>
      <input type="number" id="bulk-traffic" value="1" min="0.1" step="0.1"></div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Duration (days)</label>
      <input type="number" id="bulk-days" value="30" min="1"></div>
    <div class="form-group" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px">
      <div><label>Speed Down (KB/s)</label>
        <input type="number" id="bulk-speed-down" value="200" min="0"></div>
      <div><label>Speed Up (KB/s)</label>
        <input type="number" id="bulk-speed-up" value="200" min="0"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px">
      <div>
        <label>Numbering</label>
        <select id="bulk-numbered">
          <option value="1" selected>Numbered (001, 002, 003...)</option>
          <option value="0">Random suffix</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label>Start number</label>
        <input type="number" id="bulk-start" value="1" min="1">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px">
      <div>
        <label>Pad digits</label>
        <input type="number" id="bulk-pad" value="3" min="2" max="6">
      </div>
      <div style="padding-top:22px;color:var(--t3);font-size:11px;line-height:1.4">
        Example: <b style="color:var(--t1)">prefix-1g-001</b>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group" style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center">
      <label class="toggle" style="margin:0"><input type="checkbox" id="bulk-apply"><span class="toggle-slider"></span></label>
      <div>
        <div class="settings-label" style="font-size:13px">Apply to server now</div>
        <div class="settings-desc">May reload server config. Leave OFF to avoid any disruption.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="doBulkCreate()">Create Bulk</button>
      <button class="btn btn-danger" onclick="deleteBulkGroup()">Delete This Group</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="closeModal('bulk-modal')">Close</button>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:14px">
      <div class="settings-title">Results</div>
      <div id="bulk-tabs" class="bulk-tabs" style="display:none"></div>
      <textarea id="bulk-output" rows="10" readonly style="width:100%;padding:12px;background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);color:var(--t1);font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;resize:vertical;direction:ltr;text-align:left;word-break:break-all"></textarea>
      <div class="bulk-qr-section">
        <div class="settings-title">QR codes (all in this group)</div>
        <div id="bulk-qr-wrap" class="bulk-qr-wrap" style="display:none"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="downloadBulkZip()">Download ZIP</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="copyBulkOutput()">Copy</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="downloadBulkCSV()">Download CSV</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="openBulkInNewTab()">Open Tab</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Renew Modal ── -->
<div id="renew-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeModal(this.id)">
  <div class="modal">
    <h3>Renew: <span id="renew-name" style="color:var(--accent)"></span></h3>
    <div class="form-group"><label>New Traffic (GB)</label>
      <input type="number" id="renew-traffic" value="10" min="0.1" step="0.1"></div>
    <div class="form-group"><label>Duration (days)</label>
      <input type="number" id="renew-days" value="30" min="1"></div>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="doRenewUser()">Renew</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="closeModal('renew-modal')">Cancel</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Config Modal ── -->
<div id="config-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeModal(this.id)">
  <div class="modal modal-lg" style="max-height:calc(100vh - 40px);overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch">
    <h3>Config: <span id="config-name" style="color:var(--accent)"></span></h3>
    <div class="config-tabs" id="config-tabs" style="flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px">
      <button class="config-tab tab-vmess active" onclick="switchConfigTab('vmess')">VMess</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-vless" onclick="switchConfigTab('vless')" id="ct-vless" style="display:none">VLESS</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-cdn" onclick="switchConfigTab('cdn')" id="ct-cdn" style="display:none">CDN</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-trojan" onclick="switchConfigTab('trojan')" id="ct-trojan" style="display:none">Trojan</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-grpc" onclick="switchConfigTab('grpc')" id="ct-grpc" style="display:none">gRPC</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-httpupgrade" onclick="switchConfigTab('httpupgrade')" id="ct-httpupgrade" style="display:none">HU</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-ss2022" onclick="switchConfigTab('ss2022')" id="ct-ss2022" style="display:none">SS2022</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-vless_ws" onclick="switchConfigTab('vless_ws')" id="ct-vless_ws" style="display:none">VLESS-WS</button>
    </div>
    <div class="config-center">
      <div class="qr-box" id="config-qr"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="vmess-box">
      <label style="font-size:12px;color:var(--t3)" id="config-link-label">VMess Link</label>
      <textarea id="config-vmess" rows="3" readonly style="word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word"></textarea>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="copyConfigLink()" style="width:100%;margin-top:8px">Copy Link</button>
    </div>
    <div class="config-grid" id="config-info"></div>
    <div style="margin-top:14px;padding:12px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--t3);flex-shrink:0">📄 Sub Page:</span>
      <input type="text" id="config-sub-url" readonly style="flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:8px 10px;background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--green);font-size:11px;font-family:monospace">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="copySubUrl()" style="flex-shrink:0">Copy</button>
      <a id="config-sub-open" href="#" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" style="flex-shrink:0;text-decoration:none">Open</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:16px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="closeModal('config-modal')" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;padding:12px">Close</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Activity Modal ── -->
<div id="activity-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeActivity()">
  <div class="modal modal-lg" style="max-height:calc(100vh - 40px);overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;max-width:640px">
    <div class="activity-header">
      <h3>Activity: <span id="activity-name" style="color:var(--accent)"></span></h3>
      <span class="live-dot" id="activity-live">LIVE</span>
    </div>
    <div id="activity-alerts"></div>
    <div class="activity-tabs">
      <button class="activity-tab active" onclick="switchActivityTab('analysis')">Analysis</button>
      <button class="activity-tab" onclick="switchActivityTab('sites')">Sites</button>
      <button class="activity-tab" onclick="switchActivityTab('recent')">Recent</button>
    </div>
    <div id="activity-analysis" class="activity-body"></div>
    <div id="activity-sites" class="activity-body" style="display:none"></div>
    <div id="activity-recent" class="activity-body" style="display:none"></div>
    <div class="activity-total" id="activity-total"></div>
    <div style="margin-top:12px">
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="closeActivity()" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;padding:12px">Close</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Settings Modal ── -->
<div id="settings-modal" class="modal-overlay" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeModal(this.id)">
  <div class="modal modal-xl" style="max-height:calc(100vh - 40px);overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch">
    <h3>Settings / تنظیمات</h3>

    <!-- ═══ Settings Tabs ═══ -->
    <div class="config-tabs" style="margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <button class="config-tab tab-vmess active" onclick="switchSettingsTab('protocols')">🌐 Protocols</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-vless" onclick="switchSettingsTab('anti-dpi')">🛡️ Anti-DPI</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-cdn" onclick="switchSettingsTab('dpi-evasion')">🔬 DPI Evasion</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-trojan" onclick="switchSettingsTab('network')">☁️ Network</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-grpc" onclick="switchSettingsTab('security')">🔒 Security</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-httpupgrade" onclick="switchSettingsTab('notifications')">📨 Notifications</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-grpc2" onclick="switchSettingsTab('system')">💾 System</button>
      <button class="config-tab tab-firewall" onclick="switchSettingsTab('firewall-attacks')">⚔️ Network Resilience</button>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══ Protocols Tab ═══ -->
    <div id="settings-protocols" class="settings-tab-content">
    <!-- ═══ 1. Config Customization ═══ -->
    <div class="settings-section">
      <div class="sec-header">
        <div class="settings-title">⚙️ Config Customization</div>
        <span class="s-indicator on" id="si-vmess"><span class="dot"></span> VMess Active</span>
      </div>
      <div class="help-box">
        <div class="help-en">🔧 <b>Config names &amp; VMess base settings.</b> The prefix appears before every config name. VMess is always active on port 443 with WebSocket + TLS — the most compatible protocol.</div>
        <div class="help-fa">🔧 <b>نام کانفیگ و تنظیمات پایه VMess.</b> پیشوند قبل از نام هر کانفیگ نمایش داده می‌شه. VMess همیشه روی پورت ۴۴۳ با WebSocket + TLS فعاله — سازگارترین پروتکل.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group" style="margin-top:12px"><label>Config Name Prefix / پیشوند نام</label>
        <input type="text" id="set-config-prefix" value="Proxy" placeholder="Proxy" maxlength="20">
        <div class="settings-desc">Prefix for all config names (e.g. Proxy-username) / پیشوند نام کانفیگ‌ها (مثلاً Proxy-نام‌کاربر)</div></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>VMess Port / پورت VMess</label>
        <input type="number" id="set-vmess-port" value="443" min="1" max="65535"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>VMess SNI / Host</label>
        <input type="text" id="set-vmess-sni" placeholder="www.aparat.com">
        <div class="settings-desc">TLS Server Name — should look like a popular website / نام سرور TLS — باید شبیه یک سایت محبوب باشه</div></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>VMess WebSocket Path / مسیر وب‌سوکت</label>
        <input type="text" id="set-vmess-ws-path" value="/api/v1/stream" placeholder="/api/v1/stream">
        <div class="settings-desc">WebSocket URL path — change if default is blocked / مسیر وب‌سوکت — اگه فیلتر شده عوض کنید</div></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══ 2. Security ═══ -->
    <div class="settings-section">
      <div class="sec-header">
        <div class="settings-title">🔒 Security / امنیت</div>
        <span class="s-indicator off" id="si-ks"><span class="dot"></span> Kill Switch</span>
      </div>
      <div class="help-box">
        <div class="help-en">🛡️ <b>Kill Switch</b> automatically disables users who connect to Israel or suspicious domains. Protects your server from being flagged.</div>
        <div class="help-fa">🛡️ <b>کیل سوییچ</b> کاربرانی که به مقاصد مشکوک یا محدود وصل بشن رو خودکار غیرفعال می‌کنه. از سرورتون محافظت می‌کنه.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="settings-row">
